{
  "text": "where W m iso represents the deviatoric mechanical contribution of the tissue matrix, W f iso that of the fibers and W vol is a penalty function to enforce quasi-incompressibility. In this example, we used a strain-energy density function earlier proposed by [CITATION_1] where W vol took the form W vol \u00bc 1 D",
